title: Basil Brush Unleashed 2003
description:
Basil Brush Unleashed 2003


Basil Brush, possibly the world's most famous fox, is back. This collection contains the three episodes 'The Date', where Basil ends up on the blind date from Hell; 'Mouse', where Basil does his best to get rid of a troublesome rodent; and 'Fakes Progress', where a gypsy curse spells doom for Basil and his pals. Also includes bloopers, outtakes and jokes.
